Create Measures, New Group and Change Page Background 8

Creating Measure calculation

 Step

-       Click on a new measure

-       Put below DAX code

-   see the below GIF for more understanding 

Measure

·       % Of Correct Ans = DIVIDE([No Of Correct Ans],[Total Answer Needed Qns],0)+0

 

·       % of Not Responded Qns = DIVIDE([No. of Not Responded Qns],[Total Answer Needed Qns],0)+0

 

·       Answer Needed Qns Per Day =CALCULATE( DIVIDE([Total Answer Needed Qns],DISTINCTCOUNT('Date'[Date]),0))

 

·       Avg First Response Time = AVERAGE (ADF_Summary[AvgFirstResponseTime])

 

·       Check IsFiltered =    IF(ISFILTERED(ADF_Groups[GroupName (groups)]),1,0)

 

·       Data Color = If([First Response Hrs]>3,0,1)

 

·       Drill through button txt = SWITCH(TRUE(), SELECTEDVALUE(ADF_Groups[GroupName (groups)])<>BLANK(),"Not responded Qns in " & SELECTEDVALUE(ADF_Groups[GroupName (groups)]),SELECTEDVALUE('Date'[For the Week])<>BLANK(),"Not responded Qns for week "& SELECTEDVALUE('Date'[For the Week]),SELECTEDVALUE('Date'[DayOfWeek])<>BLANK(),"Not responded Qns in " &SELECTEDVALUE('Date'[DayOfWeek]),

    "Select to see details of not responded Qns")

 

·       First Response Hrs = AVERAGE(ADF_Summary [AvgFirstResponseTime])/60

 

·       First Response Time = SWITCH (TRUE,[Avg First Response Time] < 60, [Avg First Response Time],[Avg First Response Time] >=60 && [Avg First Response Time]<1440, [Avg First Response Time]/60 ,[Avg First Response Time]/ 1440)+0.00

 

·       No answer needed question data = if(ISBLANK([Answer Needed Qns Per Day]),"No data for the selected criteria","")

 

·       No Of Correct Ans = CALCULATE (Count(ADF_GroupQuestionComments[GroupQuestionId]),FILTER(NATURALINNERJOIN(NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(ADF_GroupQuestions,ADF_GroupQuestionComments),ADF_Groups),ADF_GroupQuestionComments[IsCorrectAnswer]=TRUE()),ADF_GroupQuestions[QuestionTypeId]=1)

 

·       No posts data = if(ISBLANK([Total Posts Per Day]),"No data for the selected criteria","")

 

·       No. of Not Responded Qns = CALCULATE([Total Answer Needed Qns],FILTER(NATURALINNERJOIN(NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(ADF_GroupQuestions,ADF_GroupQuestionComments),ADF_Groups),ADF_GroupQuestions[GroupQuestionId]<>ADF_GroupQuestionComments[GroupQuestionId]))

 

·       Previous Period Post per day = CALCULATE ([Total Posts Per Day],DATESBETWEEN('Date'[Date],[XStartOfPrevPeriod],[XEndOfPrevPeriod]),ALL('Date'[Date]))

 

·       Response HRs Goal = 3

 

·       Response Time Units = SWITCH (TRUE, [Avg First Response Time] < 60, " Min",[Avg First Response Time]>=60 && [Avg First Response Time] < 1440, " Hrs"," Days") 

 

·       Rolling Month % Changes = Var PreviousPeriodPosts = CALCULATE ([Total Posts Per Day] ,DATESBETWEEN ('Date'[Date],[XStartOfPrevPeriod],[XEndOfPrevPeriod]),ALL('Date'[Date]) )

Return

DIVIDE ([Total Posts Per Day]- PreviousPeriodPosts, PreviousPeriodPosts,0)

 

·       Selected Week title for not responded = "Questions & Not Responded % (" & SELECTEDVALUE ('Date'[For the Week],"Last 12 Weeks") &")"

 

·       Selected Week title for Posts = "Posts & Rolling Month Change (" & SELECTEDVALUE ('Date'[For the Week],"Last 12 Weeks") &")"

 

·       Selected Week Title For Qns = "Questions & First Response Time (" & SELECTEDVALUE ('Date'[For the Week],"Last 12 Weeks") &")"

 

·       Total Answer Needed Qns = CALCULATE (COUNT (ADF_GroupQuestions [GroupQuestionId]), FILTER(ADF_GroupQuestions,ADF_GroupQuestions[QuestionTypeId]=1 ))

 

·       Total Contributors = DISTINCTCOUNT (ADF_GroupQuestionComments[CreatedBy])

 

·       Total members = DISTINCTCOUNT(ADF_GroupMembers[UserId])

 

·       Total Posts = DISTINCTCOUNT(ADF_GroupQuestions[GroupQuestionId])

 

·       Total Posts Per Day = DIVIDE([Total Posts],DISTINCTCOUNT('Date'[Date]),0)

 

·       XEndOfPrevPeriod = DATEADD( PREVIOUSDAY(LASTDATE('Date'[Date])),-1,MONTH)

 

·       XStartOfPrevPeriod = DATEADD( PREVIOUSDAY(FirstDate('Date'[Date])),-1,MONTH)



Create New Group

Step: 

·       Right Click on the field

·       CTL + Select the group

·       Click group and Rename 




 

  


          Change Page Background

 

Step:

·       Click Format icon

·       Click Page background

·       Select Add image

·       Select image from the Picture
